      <hedline>
        <hl1>Introduction</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Sampling of reader responses to August 6 cover article on wrongful incarceration of Kerry Sanders as well as wrestling and rap music (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Readers were moved by our cover article on the wrongful incarceration of Kerry Sanders. The real ''three strikes and you're out,'' one wrote, is poverty, race and mental illness. Others responded to our article on wrestling and rap music with understanding of, if not approval for, the young fans.</p>
      </block>
